HEADWORD: Circumstantiality
<hw>Cir`cum*stan`ti*al"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
state, characteristic, or quality of being circumstantial; particularity
or minuteness of detail.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧I will endeavor to describe with
sufficient <xex>circumstantiality</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>De
Quincey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

